title: Vixen - Kimmy Granger (Vacation Adventures) NEW 11 October 2016
description:
Kimmy and her parents are on vacation in an exclusive resort in Southern California. The problem is, she's pretty bored and just wants some excitement. She goes back to her room to ease this by enjoying some forbidden time with a hot hotel waiter while her parents are at the pool.
